</p>

<hr />

<ul id="product-props">
    <li>Price: $9.99</li>
    <li>Artist: Van Gogh</li>
    <li>Title: </li>
    <li>Description: Self-portrait</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<div class="my-3">
    <h4 class="text-center text-info" id="demo1"></h4>
</div>

<pre>
<code>
